---
title: Pesto Baked Double Salmon with Herby Couscous and Garlicky Veggies
description: Juicy, oven-baked salmon gets topped with herby pesto and served over fluffy pearl couscous. This meal is perfect for a quick weeknight dinner or a weekend picnic at the park!
